## Savings by Tool Count

| Tools | Traditional | Meta-MCP | Savings |
|-------|-------------|----------|---------|
| 1 | 16,000 | 2,500 | **84%** |
| 2 | 16,000 | 3,200 | **80%** |
| 5 | 16,000 | 5,100 | **68%** |
| 10 | 16,000 | 8,300 | **48%** |

Formula: `1,900 + (tools × 640)`

