## Request Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant AI
  participant Meta as Meta-MCP
  participant Cache
  participant Backend

  rect rgb(230,245,255)
    Note over AI,Backend: Startup: 1.9k tokens
    AI->>Meta: (3 meta-tools loaded)
  end

  rect rgb(255,243,224)
    AI->>Meta: list_servers()
    Meta-->>AI: ["jira", "slack"]

    AI->>Meta: get_server_tools(jira, summary_only=true)
    Meta->>Backend: listTools()
    Meta-->>AI: [tool summaries]
  end

  rect rgb(232,245,233)
    Note over AI,Backend: Per tool: +640 tokens
    AI->>Meta: get_server_tools(jira, tools=["search"])
    Meta->>Cache: HIT
    Meta-->>AI: [full schema]
  end

  rect rgb(243,229,245)
    AI->>Meta: call_tool(jira, search, {...})
    Meta->>Backend: execute
    Backend-->>AI: results
  end
```

